00:52:51.418 --> 00:52:53.353 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Real faith is based on facts,

00:52:54.554 --> 00:52:56.556 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on realities,

00:52:58.525 --> 00:53:00.460 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on truth.

00:53:02.729 --> 00:53:04.731 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It gives us courage and strength,

00:53:07.434 --> 00:53:09.536 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it helps us to endure.

00:53:11.938 --> 00:53:15.508 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
